refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public Schema Objectmysql_xdevapi\Collection::getSchema




 Returns the schema object which contains the collection.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Either the schema object or null if the object cannot be retrieved for the given collection,



 this might happen if the connection has been closed for example.

  &reftitle.examples;

   mysql_xdevapi\Collection::getSchema example


<?php

//If $coll is a valid collection object, then getSchema will return the
//corresponding schema object
$schema = $coll->getSchema();

?>


